<p class="">The right hon. Gentleman no doubt wishes to be quite fair. He will remember in regard to that taunt, that in the same speech the right hon. Gentleman, the present Prime Minister, did not say one word with regard to the £1,100,000,000 due from Russia to this country.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-690d286c-f0e1-4e30-8863-94d92279f8ba" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
